      "description": "Affordable, straightforward transportation with solid everyday usefulness. This vehicle is best suited for a buyer who wants a low-cost option and appreciates a chance to own at an accessible price point. An economical choice for commuting, errands, or a backup vehicle, it delivers strong value for someone focused on budget-conscious ownership.",
