    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with plenty of life left for the right owner? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts, runs, and offers a great chance to get behind the wheel without spending a fortune. A practical choice for a commuter, first-time driver, or someone who doesn\u2019t mind a little TLC. Priced fairly and sold with honesty\u2014come take a look and see if it\u2019s the right fit for you.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid, no-nonsense driver with good bones and a strong-running powertrain. It shows cosmetic wear consistent with age, but the engine pulls well, the transmission shifts through the gears, and it tracks down the road the way it should. Suspension and braking feel serviceable, making this a practical commuter, weekend runabout, or ideal starter project for someone who wants a usable car they can improve over time. If you know how to spot value in a mechanically straightforward platform, this one deserves a look.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
